<li class="break-words"><strong>Responsiveness</strong>: Use browser dev tools to test screen sizes from 320px to 1440px. Ensure grids (<span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-200">fees-grid</span>, <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-200">payouts-grid</span>) and text remain readable.</li>
