<li class="break-words"><strong>Performance</strong>: Run Lighthouse to optimize load times. Ensure <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-200">chalkboard-plays.jpg</span> is compressed (use WebP format if possible).</li>
