<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ill include the files in <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-200">&lt;xaiArtifact&gt;</span> tags, a visual description, folder structure, and a pre-submission checklist. If you have <span class="text-sm px-1 rounded-sm !font-mono bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-500 dark:bg-orange-300/10 dark:text-orange-200">chalkboard-plays.jpg</span>, a favicon, or prefer a different background, or if you have additional payouts changes, let me know before submission.</p>
